adg.nonpostedreport.requsition

Class Requisition

  • java.lang.Object
    • adg.nonpostedreport.requsition.Requisition

  • public class Requisition
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a requisition object for the purposes of comparing and storing each requisition. Each requisition has a job code, title, location, status, requested by, and requisition owners.
    Author:
    Courtney Ripoll
